Day #11  Continual Improvement.

Continual Improvement: iterative model approach, do a gap analysis, by the customer.
Benefit: This approach helps the organization meet organization vision, It should be followed by everyone
CIR (Continual improvement Register): it is a database improvement highlighted. it is a repository for what continual improvement happens. Need to regularly assess for investment etc.
It is the responsibility of the Continual improvement Manager, to make Continual Improvement implemented properly.
